  chasing you, if you have a faster \hyperref[key:Movement
    Rate]{movement rate}, if there’s a thief in your party, if it
  rains, if it’s dark. -1 for each of the following: if there’s an elf
  or a ranger tracking you, if there are wounded party members with
  you, if there’s snow on the ground.

  Only use the modifiers if you remember.} On a 2, you’re surprised.
On a 3–6, it’s a fight. On a 7–9, choose two points from the list. On
